songs.title: Balloonatic
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Matthew Bellamy]

You came
You came, you scorched her
You came, unstained you adore her

[Chorus: Matthew Bellamy]

United again
Like separated twins
United again

[Verse 2: Matthew Bellamy]

You
You will remember
She knows, she knows you want her

[Chorus: Matthew Bellamy]

United again
Like separated twins
United again

[Chorus: Matthew Bellamy]

United again
Like separated twins
You can be...

[Outro: Matthew Bellamy]

Come gentle, slowly
Down tonight
